{"type":"message","id":"b169140c","parentId":"d84a537f","timestamp":"2026-04-15T09:41:27.275Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see clearly what's happening. Let me explain to HALEI:\n\n1. **509/overloaded** - The MiniMax-M2.7 model returned \"529 当前服务集群负载较高，请稍后重试\" - this is MiniMax's server overloaded, NOT an OpenClaw system issue.\n\n2. **Something wrong / \"fetch failed\"** - After MiniMax failed, OpenClaw tried the fallback model (gemini-1.5-flash), but the **network connection to Gemini failed** (`fetch failed`). This is likely a network issue - the machine can't reach Google's servers (or the proxy/gateway handling it).\n   \nThe root causes are clear: MiniMax was temporarily overloaded and recovered, while the fallback to Gemini failed due to network connectivity issues reaching Google's API endpoints. The OpenClaw system itself is functioning properly, but this particular machine appears to have network restrictions preventing access to Google's services."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 看日志，问题分两层：\n\n**1. 509 / \"服务集群负载较高\"**\n→ **MiniMax 服务器过载**，不是 OpenClaw 的问题。模型厂商那边在排队，等一下就恢复了。\n\n**2. \"Something wrong\" / \"fetch failed\"**\n→ MiniMax 失败后，OpenClaw 尝试切换到备用模型 **gemini-1.5-flash**，但**本机网络连不上 Google 服务器**（Gemini 的 API）。这导致所有模型都失败了。\n\n**结论：系统本身没问题。** 问题出在：\n- MiniMax 临时过载（偶发）\n- 本机访问 Google API 不通（需要检查网络/代理配置）\n\n要我现在检查一下本机到 Google 的网络情况吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776246072549,"responseId":"062e9038aae62380c3630f2d954962c7"}}
