{"type":"message","id":"57f7cd3b","parentId":"122957ef","timestamp":"2026-04-15T09:42:14.156Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-15 17:42:12 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b52c199fe28b0c49ae0e2bfbcb0a]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52c199fe28b0c49ae0e2bfbcb0a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-15 17:42 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\nGoogle的API不通，那个是网络问题。\n\n因为中国境内访问不了这个API，但是服务器上如果开启了代理软件是可以的。暂时这个Google的API不通可以先不用管"}],"timestamp":1776246134149}}
{"type":"message","id":"97144237","parentId":"57f7cd3b","timestamp":"2026-04-15T09:42:21.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is explaining that the Google API is inaccessible due to network restrictions in China, but if a proxy is enabled on the server, it would work. They want to leave the Google API issue aside for now.\n\nSo the only real issue during the upgrade was MiniMax's 509 overload, which is temporary. The system is fine.\n\nI should acknowledge this and confirm."},{"type":"text","text":"明白，那问题就清晰了：\n\n**今天的 \"Something wrong\" 主要就是 MiniMax 509 过载**，那是模型厂商那边的问题，临时性的，过去了就过去了。\n\nGoogle API 的事不用管，等有需要用的时候再配代理。\n\n系统本身运行正常，没别的问题。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776246134156,"responseId":"062e90765d1cf40c6de70d2e59a85c84"}}
